sentences.sentence: This gave me all the basic shapes for the bulkheads.
sentences.translation: 这给了我的所有基本形状为舱壁。

sentences.sentence: View looking forward inside hull, ready for bulkheads to be installed.
sentences.translation: 鉴于期待着在船体，准备舱壁安装。

sentences.sentence: Here, you can see the beginnings of the wheelhouse top with the bulkheads simply taped to the structure.
sentences.translation: 在这里，您可以看到的开端舵手顶端与舱壁录音，以简单的结构。
